Businesses today need to modernise and adjust to accommodate the growing mobile workforce in order to provide them with the flexibility they need. To do this, businesses can invest in quality devices that will allow their mobile workforce to work from anywhere in the world at any time. These devices need to offer exceptional power and versatility, so professionals can take them wherever they go to get the job done, without having to worry about a dying battery or lagging programmes. Of course, professionals also need something to complement their sleek business look, so they can close the deal at first glance. Acer’s line of business PCs offers just that. Here is a breakdown of their two best business laptops on the market, which will set you up to be an effective mobile professional. Extremely portable and versatile thanks to its 360-degree hinge, the Spin 5 Pro comes with plenty of power under the hood to let professionals work quickly and seamlessly. What’s more is it offers up to 13 hours of battery life, which means they can keeps going all day long. <img class="size-full wp-image-297852 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="374" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro-1-600x351.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Not only is it easy to carry around, but the 13-inch Spin 5 Pro packs 8th generation Intel Core processors and up to 16GB of DDR4 memory so professionals work faster and smarter. And with a battery life of up to 13 hours, they can make the most of their time. Its sleek body and gorgeous metal chassis make the Spin 5 Pro stand out from the crowd. The 360-degree hinge means that the device can work as a laptop or tablet, and in display or tent mode for creating and sharing ideas. It also contains advanced audio-visual solutions along with the optimally placed ExoAmp antenna, providing more stable wireless-Internet experienc, so that professionals can keep on top of their business communications. Below is a summary of the Spin 5 Pro’s basic features. <img class="size-full wp-image-297854 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Spin-5-Pro-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The stylish, ultra-slim, and ultra-lightweight Swift 5 Pro is perfect for busy professionals always on the go. It offers smooth usability and excellent, responsive performance. <img class="size-full wp-image-297858 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_design_ksp_02_large.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_design_ksp_02_large.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_design_ksp_02_large-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_design_ksp_02_large-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The selection of metal alloys used in the Swift 5 Pro’s build means it weighs just 970 g, while the 14.9 mm ultra-slim profile makes it easy to slip into any bag. It also features rose gold accents that add a touch of freshness to its stylish design. With 8th Generation Intel Core processors, next-generation 802.11ac 2×2 technology and battery life lasting up to 8 hours*, the Swift 5 Pro delivers the performance that professionals need to get the job done. *Battery life may vary upon usage and other conditions. While the 14-inch full HD IPS touchscreen display presents rich details and dazzling colours, Acer TrueHarmony and Dolby Audio Premium technology deliver equally brilliant sound quality. As a result, professionals can enjoy crystal clear videoconferencing and a smooth experience with Cortana. Below is a summary of the Spin 5 Pro’s basic features. Both PCs are available for purchase at www.shopacer.co.za. <img class="size-full wp-image-297856 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_features_lifestyle_large.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_features_lifestyle_large.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_features_lifestyle_large-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Acer-Swift-5_features_lifestyle_large-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />